OL,3,CNo 'significant increase' in walking
OL,4,Cand cycling in more than a decade
OL,6,FThere had been no "significant
OL,7,Fincrease" of people in Wales walking
OL,8,Fand cycling in more than a decade, a
OL,9,Fnew report has found.
OL,11,FThe Active Travel Board has called for
OL,12,Fan overhaul of data collection as well
OL,13,Fas focussing government funding on
OL,14,Fspecific areas in each local authority
OL,15,Fto ensure maximum impact.
OL,17,FBut the independent group has also
OL,18,Fpraised funding levels as well as
OL,19,F"political will" and "pioneering
OL,20,Flegislation."
