OL,6,FThe Welsh Government is aiming for
OL,7,Fthis to increase by 45% by 2040. It
OL,8,Fsaid it welcomed the report and would
OL,9,Fconsider its findings.
OL,11,FOne shop in Newport is doing their bit
OL,12,Fto make it easier and more accessible
OL,13,Ffor people to cycle around the city.
OL,15,FNewport Cycle Hub has a carpark but
OL,16,Ffor bicycles and is Wales' first 24/7
OL,17,Fstorage facility.
