OL,6,FIts owner, Mark Seymour, said: "I
OL,7,Fthink bike theft particularly in our
OL,8,Fcity centres and people travelling
OL,9,Finto work is a major concern
OL,10,Fparticularly in Wales as it isn't a
OL,11,Fvery flat nation and e-bikes for a lot
OL,12,Fof people are important for them to be
OL,13,Fable to get in and out.
OL,15,F"So having secure storage in our
OL,16,Fcentre is a vital part of our active
OL,17,Ftravel infrastructure. Otherwise, we
OL,18,Fcan built cycle routes but statistics
OL,19,Fshow that bikes are stolen.It's a
OL,20,Fbarrier for people who cycle."
