OL,6,F"We have set the ambition of becoming
OL,7,Fan active travel nation, but as yet
OL,8,Fprogress on that journey has been
OL,9,Fpainfully slow," he added.
OL,11,F"I very much hope we will be able to
OL,12,Freport on definitive progress in the
OL,13,Fyears ahead, rooted in innovative and
OL,14,Fpeople-centred research that utilises
OL,15,Finvestment in such a way as to yield
OL,16,Fdemonstrably higher levels of active
OL,17,Ftravel."
