OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, deputy chair,
OL,7,FRhiannon Letman-Wade added: "We need
OL,8,Fto have better infrastructure in
OL,9,FWales. We need to offer alternative to
OL,10,Fthe car. We need to better our public
OL,11,Ftransport and we need to offer safe
OL,12,Fwalking routes.
OL,14,F"So the report comes out with
OL,15,Fessentially nine recommendations for
OL,16,Fthe Welsh government and if we take
OL,17,Fthese recommendations then we can work
OL,18,Ftowards becoming one of the leading
OL,19,Fnations of active travel across the
OL,20,Fworld."
